{"id":1118,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":81,"title":"Conversation 41","subtitle":"Hospital Referral Discussion","level":"B1","parts":14,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-41.1118/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-41-2023-09-15-20-37-06/0-conversation-41.mp3","transcript":"All right, Mrs. Grant.\nWe're all done here.\nThe remaining tests should be done at a larger facility,\nlike the general hospital on Cambie Street.\nOh, no.\nI thought we would be able to do all of the tests right here.\nI've had multiple unpleasant experiences at the general hospital.\nI prefer the memorial hospital, to be honest.\nI'd like to help,\nbut the latest diagnostic equipment is required to perform certain tests,\nlike the ones in your case.\nLet me refer you to the memorial hospital.\nI'm sure you will be in good hands.\nThat would be great. Thanks.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:00:15","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"All right, Mrs. Grant.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-41-2023-09-15-20-37-06/1.mp3","time_start":0.4,"time_end":1.94},{"position":2,"content":"We're all done here.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-41-2023-09-15-20-37-06/2.mp3","time_start":1.94,"time_end":3.46},{"position":3,"content":"The remaining tests should be done at a larger facility,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-41-2023-09-15-20-37-06/3.mp3","time_start":3.69,"time_end":7.31},{"position":4,"content":"like the general hospital on Cambie Street.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-41-2023-09-15-20-37-06/4.mp3","time_start":7.31,"time_end":10.17},{"position":5,"content":"Oh, no.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-41-2023-09-15-20-37-06/5.mp3","time_start":10.17,"time_end":11.33},{"position":6,"content":